Commentary Text: Ravi Bishnoi to Washington Sundar, out Caught by Agarwal!! Ravi Bishnoi, in his debut IPL, bags the purple cap in the second game. Five wickets for the youngster, third of the game. Oh scratch that, actually got only one wicket in the first game. So doesn't have the cap yet. Needs one more. He nicely floats and invites the lofted hit, Sundar was tempted to back himself and go for the big hit, mistimed it to long-on. Washington Sundar c Agarwal b Ravi Bishnoi 30(27) [4s-2 6s-1]

Commentary Text: Cottrell to Kohli, out Caught by Ravi Bishnoi!! Bangalore pressing the self destruct button now. This shot from Kohli reminds me of his dismissal in the 2015 WC semis. A left-armer digging it short and getting the better of him thanks to an ungainly top-edge. This was caught easily at mid-on. That was short and angled across after a couple of fuller deliveries. Nicely set up by the bowler. He bent his back on this delivery and got his reward. Kohli c Ravi Bishnoi b Cottrell 1(5)
